Function to recode weight variable

Source: R/03-recode_anthro.R
recode_weight.Rd

Function to recode weight variable

recode_weight(df)

Arguments

df

A data.frame collected for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Study containing anthropometric data

Value

A vector of recoded weights based on any re-testing done

Examples


recode_weight(df = childAnthro)
